(- Optionally accepts an LLM-assisted plan when available and valid.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Executor) Tj
T*
(- Uses provided artifacts first.) Tj
T*
(- Optionally collects missing evidence live with whitelisted commands.) Tj
T*
(- Normalizes and parses outputs into structured intermediate representations.) Tj
T*
(- Builds topology snapshot \(gateway, routes, neighbors, hops, interfaces\).) Tj
T*
(- Supports configurable live capture duration \(default 30s, user override via CLI or prompt\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Generator) Tj
T*
(- Produces Diagnosis object:) Tj
T*
(- problem summary) Tj
T*
(- ranked candidate causes) Tj
T*
(- confidence score) Tj
T*
(- required evidence) Tj
T*
(- remediation plan) Tj
T*
(- Uses deterministic heuristics by default.) Tj
T*
(- Optionally switches to LLM-assisted diagnosis generation with schema checks/fallback.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Validator) Tj
T*
(- Enforces structural and numeric checks.) Tj
T*
(- Applies safety gate to proposed commands.) Tj
T*
(- Marks ambiguous cases and can invoke optional LLM critic.) Tj
T*
(- Treats LLM verdict as advisory; safety gate and deterministic constraints remain) Tj
T*
(authoritative.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Cross-cutting infrastructure) Tj
T*
(- SafetyGate: command allowlists, forbidden tokens, mutation-token approval checks.) Tj
T*
(- AuditLogger: JSONL trace per stage.) Tj
T*
(- Debug trace: request-scoped operation inputs/outputs/timings.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Multi-LLM Call Flow) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The project uses multiple LLM-capable interaction points with explicit roles.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(LLM roles) Tj
T*
(- Planner LLM \(optional\)) Tj
T*
(- Input: user prompt + artifact preview + host OS.) Tj
T*
(- Output schema: category, selected_checks, rationale.) Tj
T*
(- Validation: category and check whitelist normalization; fallback to deterministic planner if) Tj
T*
(invalid.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Generator LLM \(optional\)) Tj
T*
(- Input: selected checks, parsed outputs, missing checks, topology, user prompt.) Tj
T*
(- Output schema: diagnosis payload with ranked causes and remediation.) Tj
T*
(- Validation: cause list non-empty, confidence clamping, fallback remediation/evidence defaults.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Validator LLM Critic \(optional and conditional\)) Tj
T*
