(- Trigger: low confidence or high ambiguity.) Tj
T*
(- Input: diagnosis summary + execution context.) Tj
T*
(- Output schema: verdict, confidence, notes, suggested_evidence.) Tj
T*
(- Handling: reject/caution becomes validation reasons; cannot bypass safety gate.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Intermediate representations) Tj
T*
(The pipeline relies on explicit typed/dict structures between stages:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- PlannerPlan) Tj
T*
(- ExecutionResult \(raw outputs, parsed outputs, missing checks, topology\)) Tj
T*
(- Diagnosis) Tj
T*
(- ValidationResult) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(LLM outputs are treated as untrusted until parsed, shape-checked, normalized, and optionally) Tj
T*
(clamped.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Coordination strategy) Tj
T*
(The coordination model is linear with hard boundaries:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Planner commits check set.) Tj
T*
(- Executor resolves artifact/live data and parsing.) Tj
T*
(- Generator ranks causes using evidence.) Tj
T*
(- Validator checks constraints and confidence behavior.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This avoids hidden side effects and keeps debugging straightforward because each stage has) Tj
T*
(explicit inputs and outputs logged to audit/debug channels.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Tools and APIs Used) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Core implementation tools) Tj
T*
(- Python package modules in src/network_agent/.) Tj
T*
(- Regex-based parsers for ping, traceroute, logs, pcap summary.) Tj
T*
(- Dataclasses for contracts and serialization.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Local and optional LLM connectors) Tj
T*
(- mock provider \(deterministic/testing\).) Tj
T*
(- ollama provider for offline local inference.) Tj
T*
(- openai and openai_compatible for API-compatible backends.) Tj
T*
(- anthropic support in critic path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(System diagnostics / shell tools) Tj
T*
(- ping, traceroute/tracert, nslookup, netstat, route, arp, interface info commands.) Tj
T*
(- tcpdump for read-only capture on supported non-Windows hosts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Development/test tooling) Tj
T*
(- pytest for unit-style checks.) Tj
T*
(- Synthetic sample fixtures in samples/.) Tj
T*
(- Cross-platform CI configuration \(Linux/macOS/Windows matrix in repository workflow\).) Tj
T*
