() Tj
T*
(- Offline usability improved) Tj
T*
(   Local model startup wrappers \(.sh + .bat\) and GUI/CLI launchers support constrained) Tj
T*
(environments.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Cross-platform practical fixes were incorporated) Tj
T*
(   Windows-specific issues \(launcher behavior, import path setup, decode handling, ping timeout) Tj
T*
(bounds\) were addressed with targeted changes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Measured outcome snapshot) Tj
T*
(Using demo.py, three end-to-end interactions were executed with full agent loop and debug trace:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- dns_failure -> category dns, top cause DNS resolution failure.) Tj
T*
(- connectivity_loss -> category connectivity, top cause High packet loss indicates unstable or) Tj
T*
(broken link.) Tj
T*
(- transport_retransmits -> category transport, top cause Transport congestion or drops causing) Tj
T*
(retransmissions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Artifacts and traces are included under examples/interactions/.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Failure modes observed) Tj
T*
(- Incomplete/malformed pcap summary reduces transport-confidence quality.) Tj
T*
(- Extremely sparse artifacts may force low-confidence generic diagnosis.) Tj
T*
(- Live capture commands can fail due to permission/environment limitations.) Tj
T*
(- LLM output schema drift can occur on unsupported or poorly tuned local models \(handled via) Tj
T*
(fallback, but still a UX limitation\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Tradeoffs and design decisions) Tj
T*
(- Conservative safety over broad command freedom: fewer dangerous operations, but less automated) Tj
T*
(remediation.) Tj
T*
(- Linear agent pipeline over dynamic planner-executor loops: easier to reason about and test,) Tj
T*
(but less adaptive in long investigations.) Tj
T*
(- Strict schema checks over permissive parsing: more robust behavior under unexpected LLM) Tj
T*
(outputs, but occasional fallback to heuristic path.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Limitations and Extensions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Current limitations) Tj
T*
(- No deep packet parsing beyond summary signals.) Tj
T*
(- No integration with external telemetry backends \(Prometheus/Grafana/cloud APIs\) yet.) Tj
T*
(- Root-cause confidence remains heuristic and not calibrated with a large empirical corpus.) Tj
T*
(- Live capture on Windows is limited by tooling differences.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Near-term extensions) Tj
T*
(- Add richer packet/event parsers \(e.g., mtr, iperf3, DNS trace depth\).) Tj
T*
(- Add redaction pipeline for sensitive logs/artifacts.) Tj
T*
(- Implement confidence calibration on labeled incident datasets.) Tj
T*
(- Add iterative clarification loop when evidence is insufficient.) Tj
T*
