T*
(- Conclusion) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(network-agent demonstrates a practical multi-agent architecture for network diagnostics with) Tj
T*
(explicit safety controls, auditable execution, and optional local/offline LLM assistance. The) Tj
T*
(system is not designed as a free-form autonomous operator; instead, it is a constrained) Tj
T*
(diagnostic partner that prioritizes traceability and correctness under uncertainty. This design) Tj
T*
(choice made the project robust, testable, and suitable for instructional evaluation while) Tj
T*
(leaving clear paths for future research extensions.) Tj
T*
